        <div class="pf-step"><div class="pf-step-num">4</div><div><strong>Inhibitor topped up and system balanced</strong><p>The inhibitor concentration is checked and topped up before refilling. Once the system is back on, every radiator is balanced to deliver the correct heat output. This step is critical for even heating throughout the property and is included on every job we do.</p></div></div>
